      * Test: MOVE CORRESPONDING between groups. Expected output: ALICE then 030
       IDENTIFICATION DIVISION.
       PROGRAM-ID. MOVE-CORRESPONDING-TEST.
       DATA DIVISION.
       WORKING-STORAGE SECTION.
       01 WS-SRC-GROUP.
           05 WS-NAME PIC X(5) VALUE "ALICE".
           05 WS-AGE  PIC 9(3) VALUE 030.
           05 WS-EXTRA PIC X(4) VALUE "XTRA".
       01 WS-DST-GROUP.
           05 WS-NAME PIC X(5).
           05 WS-AGE  PIC 9(3).
       PROCEDURE DIVISION.
       MAIN-PARA.
           MOVE CORRESPONDING WS-SRC-GROUP TO WS-DST-GROUP
           DISPLAY WS-NAME OF WS-DST-GROUP
           DISPLAY WS-AGE OF WS-DST-GROUP
           STOP RUN.
